{"name": "Ctrl + Alt + Mint 1", "description": "Control-Alt-Mint (often abbreviated to Ctrl+Alt+Mint, also known as the "three-finger mint" or "Mint Keys") is a computer keyboard command on Ethereum compatible computers, invoked by pressing the Mint key while holding the Control and Alt keys: Ctrl+Alt+Mint. 

The function of the key combination differs depending on the context but it generally mints a great piece of art, an idea, and/or anything and everything else. Starting with Ethereum, the key combination invokes a mint function or mint related component that facilitates minting an edition, a drop, or a single token.

Enjoy!
